   "source": [
    "# MCF7 Probabilistic Archetype Trajectory Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "Trajectory-style analysis in archetype simplex space with explicit run selection by `K`, model type, and decoder type.\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook treats archetypes as attractor-like basin anchors and reports:\n",
    "- state-space geometry (PCA/UMAP on simplex weights)\n",
    "- basin depth / instability proxies\n",
    "- archetype-pair corridor occupancy (transition surrogate graph)\n",
    "- pair-progress and kNN geodesic pseudotime analogs\n",
    "- robustness across top-N selected runs\n",
    "\n",
    "Important caveat: this is trajectory-like structure from static data, not direct dynamical inference.\n"
   ]
  },
